verse = \lyricmode {
  \"I do not need your goats or your young bulls;
I will not take them from your pens and stalls.
Mine are the cat -- tle on a thou -- sand hills,
mine ev -- ery beast that in the for -- est dwells.
All birds, all an -- i -- mals in field and pas -- ture
be -- long to me, their ma -- ker and their mas -- ter.
}
